'From Squeak3.4alpha of 6 November 2002 [latest update: #5132] on 24 November 2002 at 1:56:14 pm'!"Change Set:		conChkOops-swDate:			24 November 2002Author:			Scott WallaceRemoves (in the postscript) a method erroneously added in a preliminary internal version of update 5128.  It was my error that that code, intended for inclusion in the external conflict-checker package, was published"!"Postscript:"((Smalltalk allImplementorsOf: #conflictsWithUpdatedMethods:) size = 0)	ifTrue:		[FilePackage class removeSelector: #fileReaderServicesForFile:suffix:].!